node.text:
At 20 years old I packed up my entire life in Kentucky to serve in this Administration and to fight for the American people. It has been the honor of my life standing alongside President Donald J. Trump and to be a voice for forgotten Americans. He pushed me to stand firm in my convictions and his courage was contagious. 

Mr. President, it has been a privilege implementing your agenda in the Presidential Personnel Office. Only in your America could I go from working in a gym to working in the White House, because that is the American dream you envisioned for our youth. I am eternally grateful 45.
